{"tid":354920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發，多難興邦】陝西旅遊巴撞車，36死","createTime":"2017-08-11T01:10:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-11T02:02:55.000Z","uid":35221,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8faddd048a52e826e4f616b6376cc2c942442013","tid":354920,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T01:10:42.000Z","msg":"突发！京昆高速安康段发生大客车碰撞隧道事故，致36人死亡<br />\n<br />\n2017-08-11&nbsp;新华社<br />\n<br />\n8月10日23时许，陕西省境内京昆高速公路安康段秦岭1号隧道发生一起大客车碰撞隧道口事故，造成车内36人死亡，13人受伤。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n目前伤者已送往当地医院救治，事故调查工作正在进行中。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事故发生后，国务委员、公安部部长郭声琨高度重视，立即做出指示，要求迅速查明事故原因，尽最大努力抢救伤员，并派出由公安部党委副书记、副部长黄明带队的工作组立即赶赴现场指导事故调查处置工作。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n来源：新华社<br />\n<br />\n记者：刘奕湛、陈晨<br />\n<br />\n监制：葛素表<br />\n<br />\n编辑：关开亮、赵刚、陈子夏"},{"pid":"1c5d3d0a551a688b0db8de7126a413dfd94d3601","tid":354920,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T01:15:18.000Z","msg":"陝西長途巴撞車36死13傷 (08:54)<br />\n<br />\n2017/8/11<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170811/s00004/14140381f666b8400de508f21c9c6a74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170811%2Fs00004%2F14140381f666b8400de508f21c9c6a74.jpg&h=842214cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陝西昨晚11時34分發生嚴重車禍，一架長途巴士由四川成都駛往河南洛陽途中，經過京崑高速公路西安方向秦嶺一號隧道南口時，撞向隧道口，釀成車上36人死亡，包括26名男子、8名女子以及2名兒童，另有13人受傷。傷者已送往醫院救治，事故原因正在調查中。公安部黨委副書記、副部長黃明率領工作組趕赴現場處理。<br />\n<br />\n(綜合)<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170811/s00004/1502412529879\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170811%2Fs00004%2F1502412529879&d=vOTBSNjuBlgphOHGkzXh6W6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=095dee05\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170811%2Fs00004%2F1502412529879&h=c0cb28df\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170811/s00004/1502412529879</a>"},{"pid":"e6c2fd2611067f0e3378b43ee02999fd6ba31061","tid":354920,"uid":35221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T01:16:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170811/s00004/1413e915a6ace7b63901c90389e1af5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170811%2Fs00004%2F1413e915a6ace7b63901c90389e1af5a.jpg&h=1f08ee45&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"18c14a944c28bb6d46607281957f54a75ef88428","tid":354920,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T01:21:01.000Z","msg":"多左1 個人既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a515bea6e9b3c654face62b9d7a284051bae8b42","tid":354920,"uid":43721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T01:21:36.000Z","msg":"撞擊測試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7e16157465d217778f434cdc6d0f7086791678d","tid":354920,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T01:22:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多左1 個人既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n反了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74be59027cfcc37daa4ef3109cf2de14a8ad00c2","tid":354920,"uid":759,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T01:24:04.000Z","msg":"死多d<br />\n多d黎密d死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nall go to hell<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c66380679123c3e2f860cf9e867712c4d839347c","tid":354920,"uid":55868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T01:25:30.000Z","msg":"撞車死亡數字比地震高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df21f367b98cd590a0942c38a8b04245f8e628da","tid":354920,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T01:26:04.000Z","msg":"陝西重大車禍　隧道中巴士撞牆釀36死<br />\n<br />\n2017/08/11 08:24&nbsp;7360<br />\n<br />\n中國陝西省昨（10日）深夜發生重大車禍，一輛客運車在高速公路隧道中撞牆，造成36人死亡、13人受傷。新華社報導，10日晚間11時34分許，西漢高速陝西段發生一起交通事故，初步瞭解，事故車輛為河南經營的一輛客運車，從成都發往洛陽，在途經西漢高速公路秦嶺隧道時，因撞到隧道牆壁發生事故，事故造成36人死亡，13人受傷，傷者已被緊急送醫。<br />\n<br />\n中新網報導，這輛客車為2011年12月19日出廠，檢驗有效期至2018年1月31日，核載51人，實載49人。死者中包括34名成人（男26人、女8人），以及2名男女兒童。秦嶺隧道由眾多隧道組成，全長近12公里，有中國網友表示通過需要近半小時。　（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170811/1179953/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170811%2F1179953%2F&d=vOTBSNjuBlgphOHGkzXh6W6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=795b402a\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170811/1179953/</a>"},{"pid":"9218c03d480d900b95f4578211f81f1e84bfaa83","tid":354920,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T01:26:54.000Z","msg":"幾年前去過，條隧道真係好撚長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170811/640_31e5da8c9ee0021eec1d9f4180274ccd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170811%2F640_31e5da8c9ee0021eec1d9f4180274ccd.jpg&h=43250218&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7fcf9c2fcbd0e41ae56beb55d2ac961679c37650","tid":354920,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T01:27:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170811/640_b3e3f97dfdd8f9767a1b159d1dc1833b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170811%2F640_b3e3f97dfdd8f9767a1b159d1dc1833b.jpg&h=2404c8cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"99f8f2b70e0e92ab3bba609de70fe7067e5b8211","tid":354920,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,