sg":"大陸公路d燈好暗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25a62729d16d13dde68c280fc461d510c78301dd","tid":354920,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T01:56:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大陸公路d燈好暗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好多都係無燈，即係有裝通風同燈但唔撚開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a87a1e9b6688cf9a8304a1cb80efd8ae465ac4e9","tid":354920,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T01:58:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲以為跌埋落去先死咁多 原來只係撞牆 真不愧為蝗蟲 一撞就死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好難明點樣死咁多。</blockquote><br />\n睇架車撞成咁,似係高速炒埋去"},{"pid":"fcb9813008d89b7fdd31374ec28026069a50d7f8","tid":354920,"uid":759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T02:01:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>仲以為跌埋落去先死咁多 原來只係撞牆 真不愧為蝗蟲 一撞就死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好難明點樣死咁多。</blockquote><br />\n睇架車撞成咁,似係高速炒埋去</blockquote><br />\n又無反無爆<br />\n坐車後面都撞死果d 好難理解"},{"pid":"b3851e1ea12ae6450d4b41a1275528c3195fffa3","tid":354920,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T02:02:55.000Z","msg":"竟然唔係三十五死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n反了反了！！！"}]}